<li><strong>Filecoin (FIL)</strong>: A decentralized storage network built on blockchain technology, Filecoin allows users to rent out their unused storage space.</li>



<li><strong>Uniswap (UNI)</strong>: Uniswap is a decentralized exchange protocol running on the Ethereum blockchain, enabling users to swap ERC-20 tokens seamlessly.</li>
