<p>Coinbase provides strong customer support through various channels such as email and live chat.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Stablecoin and Lending Services</h3>



<p>Coinbase offers&nbsp;<a href="https://milkroad.com/lend/stablecoins/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">stablecoin and lending services</a>, allowing users to earn interest on certain stablecoins like USD Coin (USDC). With a US bank account, users can redeem 1 USDC for $1.00, making it a reliable and secure option for those looking to stabilize their cryptocurrency holdings.</p>



<p>Coinbase provides lending services where users can borrow against their crypto assets instead of selling them. This allows traders to access funds while still holding onto their digital assets, potentially avoiding taxable events or missing out on future price increases.</p>



<p>By offering these stablecoin and lending services, Coinbase gives its users more flexibility and opportunities to maximize the value of their cryptocurrencies in 2023.</p>



