<li>The Kraken trading platform can be overwhelming for new users, with a steep learning curve required to navigate all the features effectively.</li>



<li>Advanced trading options such as margin and futures trading available in the Kraken Pro platform may be too complicated for beginners, and itâ€™s important to understand these features before using them.</li>
